CHANGELOG
============

2018.04.05

    Update documentation

2018.02.27

    Add option "count" to include image number in index
    Add option "count_dir" to include directories number in index (including links, but excluding hidden dirs)

2017.12.05

    Add -r option to automatically rename img_* files to i%Y%m%d_%H%M%S. Todo: make pattern configurable

2016.09.17

    Compatibility with Perl 5.22, fix "Can't use a hash as a reference" error

2016.07.29

    Get rid of date on index pages
    Add -s option to sync after generating the gallery

2014.11.28

    Added reverse sort: r+glob

2014.08.03

    Proper "deep" cloning of object via Storage
    Check if -u parameter has valid value

